headline: Henry Schein One Unveils The Catalyst Index, a Look into Dentistry’s Top 10%
summary: AMERICAN FORK, Utah, May 20, 2025--Henry Schein One today announced the launch of The 2025 Catalyst Index, its exclusive report offering dental practices an unparalleled view into the strategies transforming performance across the industry. Built on years of trusted benchmarking and informed by Henry Schein One’s most connected platform, the fourth annual report, The Catalyst Index, raises the bar by revealing the specific actions that distinguish the top 10% of DSOs and private practices.
